videos.description: Nathan Adrian comes up with the steal before Jevon Carter finds Esa Ahmad who finishes the dunk.
videos.headline: WVU's steal leads to powerful dunk by Ahmad

videos.description: Daxter Miles Jr. keeps his feet inbounds and makes the nice lay-in for West Virginia.
videos.headline: WVU's Miles Jr. stays inbounds and makes the reverse layup

videos.description: Niem Stevenson catches the defender with the ball fake and then drains the 3-pointer for Texas Tech.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Stevenson with nice ball fake before draining 3-pointer

videos.description: Sagaba Konate gets the steal and then finishes with the dunk.
videos.headline: Defense leads to offense for WVU

videos.description: Jevon Carter makes the Texas Tech defender jump before draining a shot for West Virginia.
videos.headline: WVU's Carter fools defender then drains turn-around jumper

videos.description: Keenan Evans brings the ball up the court and drains the 3-pointer over a  West Virginia defender for Texas Tech.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Evans drains 3-pointer to send game into OT

videos.description: Off the miss by Jevon Carter, Daxter Miles Jr. comes out of nowhere and gets the tip-in to go in for West Virginia.
videos.headline: Miles Jr. with the tip-in shot to extend WVU's lead in 2nd OT

videos.description: Nathan Adrian misses the jumper, but Daxter Miles Jr. comes flying in for the putback dunk for West Virginia.
videos.headline: Miles Jr. finishes with putback dunk in 2OT win

videos.description: Breaking down the play of Eiljah Macon and how West Virginia came out with a victory over Texas Tech.
videos.headline: Bob Wischusen and Fran Fraschilla on Elijah Macon's key play
